Comic-Con Festival 2018 started with fans trooping to San Diego, the venue for this year’s festival, wearing their favourite comic character suits. The festival has been attended by Hollywood actors with celebrities like Johny Depp who featured in Fantastic Beasts, Jason Mamoa who plays Aquaman in the DC film. Aquaman will be officially released on December 21. View the trailer below   Gal Gadot and Chris Pine who played Wonderwoman and Steve Trevor in the Film Wonderwoman made an appearance. The upcoming sequel to Wonderwoman was discussed but they didn’t give away any secrets or any spoilers. Fans are already buzzing and anticipating the sequel although it might take close to a year before filming will be completed.